---
import SubpageLayout from "../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro";
import BackButton from "../../components/BackButton.astro";
---

<SubpageLayout title="Team | About | Yangs AI" description="Introduction to the YangsAI team.">
	<BackButton href="/" label="Back to Home" />
	<p class="font-tech mt-5 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-zinc-300">Yangs AI</p>
	<h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-100 md:text-5xl">About Team</h1>
	<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
		The YangsAI team brings together researchers and engineers focused on foundational AI principles,
		reproducible resources, and benchmark-centered evaluation.
	</p>

	<div class="mt-10 grid gap-4">
		<a
			href="/team/members"
			class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 p-6 transition hover:border-white/30 hover:bg-white/10"
		>
			<p class="font-tech text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-300">Team</p>
			<p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-100">Members</p>
			<p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-sm text-zinc-300">
				Browse team profiles maintained as markdown pages for fast updates to bios, interests, and contributions.
			</p>
			<p class="font-tech mt-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-200">Visit Track</p>
		</a>

		<a
			href="https://jason-young.me"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noreferrer"
			class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 p-6 transition hover:border-white/30 hover:bg-white/10"
		>
			<p class="font-tech text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-300">Team</p>
			<p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-100">Founder</p>
			<p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-sm text-zinc-300">
				Learn more about the founder's academic background, publications, and current research activities.
			</p>
			<p class="font-tech mt-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-200">Visit Profile</p>
		</a>
	</div>
</SubpageLayout>
